SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT 'SALDO' DESCRIPTION, ':1' DocDate, NULL DocNum, '' ItemCode, '' ItemName, '' DistNumber,'' WhsCode,'' Consignee, SUM(Qty) Qty, SUM(Qty2) Qty2, SUM(DocTotal) DocTotal,'' CardName, '' BinCode FROM ItemHistory I WHERE ItemName LIKE '%:4%' AND DocDate < ':1' :3 :5 :6 UNION ALL SELECT DESCRIPTION,I.DocDate,I.DocNum, I.ItemCode,I.ItemName,I.DistNumber,I.WhsCode,U_IDU_Kode_PT Consignee,Qty,Qty2, DocTotal,CardName,BinCode FROM ItemHistory I LEFT JOIN sys_gcm ON condition='OBJTYPE' AND GCM_ID=ObjType LEFT JOIN OBIN on BinAbs=OBIN.AbsEntry WHERE Docdate BETWEEN ':1' AND ':2' AND I.ItemName LIKE '%:4%' :3 :5 :6 UNION ALL SELECT 'TOTAL' DESCRIPTION, ':2' DocDate, NULL DocNum, '' ItemCode, '' ItemName, '' DistNumber,'' WhsCode,'' Consignee, SUM(Qty) Qty, SUM(Qty2) Qty2, SUM(DocTotal) DocTotal,'' CardName, '' BinCode FROM ItemHistory I WHERE ItemName LIKE '%:4%' AND DocDate <= ':2' :3 :5 :6

ExpSyntax.val: IF(ISNULL({0,28}) OR {0,28}=-1,' AND I.BplID in (Select BplID from USR6 where UserId = '&Trim(Str({32768,1},'10'))&' ) ',' AND BplId = '&Trim(Str({0,28},''))&' ')
